            <title>[LU-11304] URLs need be updated </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11304</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Looking at current codes, still many places for example README, man page etc still&lt;br/&gt;
